name: Pyrtemonnaie
tagline: Python tool to organize your monthly costs
body:
### What is pyrtemonnaie?

Pyrtemonnaie is a wip tool to collect your monthly costs in a simple and intuitive way.
Its build on python and uses pyqt to generate a qt-bases ui.

As this is wip and I'm using this to learn python, this project is highly experimental.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
